## Step 3: Editor Basics

This step has a skip gate and then two parts: a hands-on lesson navigating the workspace, followed by an explanation of the chat panel and how we work together.

### 3-gate: Skip Detection

Since the user got this far via the chat, they clearly know the basics. Offer a skip option before diving into editor teaching.

